{"tid":99180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港獨立 突發] 雞年車公籤文指香港會「自興家」","createTime":"2017-01-29T04:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T07:49:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9f7a36021de7467cdee1601b0c0e46e787d1d39","tid":99180,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:02:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170129/56237070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170129%2F56237070&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=cb2a5b42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170129%2F56237070&h=82f7b3fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170129/56237070</a><br />\n<br />\n 【新增影片】<br />\n今年第二年由經民聯劉皇發兒子、鄉議局主席劉業強率領一眾鄉紳包括副主席林偉強，以及立法會議員包括新民黨容海恩及民建聯周浩鼎等，前年被舞麒麟撞倒的特首參選人葉劉淑儀亦有出席，靠站在一旁。劉業強在車公廟代表鄉議局為香港求籤，繼去年為香港求得上籤，劉業強今年求得61籤上籤，籤文為「傳來信息果無差，轉運時來自興家；篤志雲程須著力，何天今日賜榮華。」籤文解曰，凡事吉利。<br />\n<br />\n劉業強其後向香港市民祝福萬事大吉，並請解籤師傅解述籤文。解籤師傅說，籤文解曰香港今年會有一些好的信息，好的轉變，好的運勢，會轉運時來，局勢會向好發展，只要市民及政府一齊努力，香港會繼續繁榮穩定。<br />\n<br />\n劉業強被問到特首選舉，他指知道市民都關注特首選舉，認為任何一位新特首都會新景象，籲社會各界拋開矛盾成見，官民合作。被問到是否支持前政務司司長林鄭朋娥，劉指現時言之過早，會與每一位候選人會面，溝通後再作決定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170129/large/1485652869_d8c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170129%2Flarge%2F1485652869_d8c2.jpg&h=9fc34722&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60f3e8ebd0e31ca978a71c3f825afbb033eac572","tid":99180,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:03:30.000Z","msg":"劉業強在車公廟代表鄉議局為香港求籤！<br />\n<br />\n關乜鬼特首事？<br />\n<br />\n根本就係講緊香港會自興家！會獨立！<br />\n<br />\n傳來信息果無差，轉運時來自興家；<br />\n篤志雲程須著力，何天今日賜榮華。"},{"pid":"3ce817d423ecd921fec69e5ba155c4455a765cbe","tid":99180,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:05:10.000Z","msg":"籤文解曰，凡事吉利。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港獨立！<br />\n國泰民安！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.hknationalparty.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/%E6%8F%AE%E6%98%A5_icon-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.hknationalparty.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F%25E6%258F%25AE%25E6%2598%25A5_icon-1.jpg&h=dad7cdc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e373e6093ff71142717ac5325e49a183061cd71","tid":99180,"uid":2087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b8e027edbf13d080ba1eab565e2a3e935c9b7c","tid":99180,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:09:51.000Z","msg":"香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078997986eb084b755cade41d8b70e35e9af4389","tid":99180,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:10:36.000Z","msg":"劉王叔，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d06c65fd5f90e92b06d78fe9ee6f9b06e2b4466","tid":99180,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"志雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64790cb57ce41d543b66def2effa8d2843251ec","tid":99180,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:15:31.000Z","msg":"傳來信息果無差 = 之前對支爆既判斷無錯, 果無差<br />\n<br />\n轉運時來自興家 = 趁住支爆, 香港就會獨立、自興家<br />\n<br />\n篤志雲程須著力 = 對於獨立既志向, 仍有路要走, 一定要盡力<br />\n<br />\n何天今日賜榮華 = 他日成功, 香港人自獲上天賜榮華<br />\n<br />\n籤文解曰，凡事吉利。<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立, 上上籤！<br />\n<br />\n講得好明, 三歲都識睇識解啦！"},{"pid":"52519dc944fe7791153177ab2c229b6ffc2806b8","tid